# Security Model

The platform implements modern cryptographic standards.

Core technologies include:

- End-to-End Encryption
- X3DH
- Double Ratchet
- Curve25519
- HKDF
- AES-256-GCM
- TLS 1.3

Enterprise security capabilities are designed to complement, not replace, organizational security policies.

